<LocalizedProperties><Language>en</Language><Title>Q324380: Security Update (Windows 2000)</Title><Description>This update resolves the "Weak Encryption in RDP Protocol can Lead to Information Disclosure" security vulnerability in Windows 2000. Download now if you use Remote Desktop or Terminal Services, to help prevent an attacker from potentially learning encrypted information that was sent during Remote Desktop or Terminal Services sessions.</Description><MoreInfoUrl>http://www.download.windowsupdate.com/msdownload/update/v3/static/RTF/en/5476.htm</MoreInfoUrl><SupportUrl>http://support.microsoft.com</SupportUrl></LocalizedProperties>